{
  "id": "adv_card_ktn_10_02",
  "title": "長瀬琴乃",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんの誕生日にライブをやるなら\n一つ、お願いしたいことがあります",
      "startTime": 3.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "私がお姉ちゃんの誕生日をお祝いしたのは\n遊園地に一緒に行ったのが最後でした",
      "startTime": 10.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "その後はお姉ちゃん、仕事が忙しくなっちゃって\n……私も意地を張って、お姉ちゃんとろくに話さなくて",
      "startTime": 18.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "私が行かなかったバースデーライブのことも\nお姉ちゃんがいろいろ話してくれたんですけど",
      "startTime": 26.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "びっくりするくらい大きなケーキが用意してあったとか\nペンライトがハートの形になって綺麗だった、とか",
      "startTime": 35.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あの時は遙子さんが、凄く頑張ってくれたからな",
      "startTime": 39.5086169717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "……そうみたいですね。遙子さんに聞きました\nでもあの頃の私は、それも凄く腹が立って",
      "startTime": 48.5333340962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "私と一緒に遊園地に行ったのなんか\nきっと、しょぼかったと思ってるんだろうって",
      "startTime": 57.6333340962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことはないよ\n麻奈は琴乃と誕生日を過ごしたがってたし",
      "startTime": 63.2333340962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "……はい。あれはただのつまらない意地だったって\n今なら思えます",
      "startTime": 71.4333340962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "あの時、お姉ちゃんに寂しい思いをさせてしまったので\nだから、今からでもおめでとうって言いたいんです",
      "startTime": 78.8666674296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "だから、そのライブで……十月九日にあるライブで\nお姉ちゃんの曲を歌わせてもらうことは出来ませんか？",
      "startTime": 89.5333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどな。もちろん大歓迎だ\n……麻奈も、きっと喜ぶと思う",
      "startTime": 97.3666669209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "……！　ありがとうございます\nお姉ちゃんに胸を張れるように、頑張ります",
      "startTime": 104.6666669209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 108.9999987284
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ふう……さすがに打ち合わせが三件続くと疲れるな\nん？　そこのソファに誰か……琴乃？",
      "startTime": 116.0000002543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "すー、すー……",
      "startTime": 121.8351228232,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……琴乃、琴乃\nこんなところで寝てたら、風邪引くぞ",
      "startTime": 137.4333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "……え、{user}さん！？\nもしかして私、ここで寝ちゃってたんですか！？",
      "startTime": 144.2666669209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "今日は午後からずっとレッスンだったので\nちょっとだけ休んでから帰ろうと思って……",
      "startTime": 151.7666552226,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "いつもの仕事にライブの準備もあるもんな\n疲れてるなら、来週のスケジュールを調整しようか？",
      "startTime": 158.6999885559,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、大丈夫です。そこまで無茶はしてませんから",
      "startTime": 162.1143841101,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "それに、お姉ちゃんの誕生日に\nステージでみっともない歌を歌う訳にはいきませんし",
      "startTime": 169.9666552226,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 11866.666666599996,
          "startTime": 181.8333218892
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "でも、今日はもう寮に戻って早めに休みますね\nそれでは、失礼します",
      "startTime": 179.0666572571,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "少しふらついてるのは、寝ぼけてるだけじゃないよな\nあれは大分疲れが溜まってるな……",
      "startTime": 188.8999946594,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "まったく……ステージのために無茶しがちなところは\n麻奈とそっくりだ",
      "startTime": 196.8000007629,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 20833.321126300005,
          "startTime": 217.6333218892
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 199.6000007629
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-ktn018.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……またターンが半テンポ遅れてる……\nもう一回、次は気持ち早めに足を出して……",
      "startTime": 215.1333218892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃、まだ残ってたんだな\n夕方に収録を終えてから、ずっと練習してたのか？",
      "startTime": 223.0999885559,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "もう、大分遅い時間だぞ\nその様子だと、夕飯もまだ食べてないんだろう",
      "startTime": 229.4999885559,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-ktn019.m4a",
      "text": "そう言えば忘れてました\n……思い出したら、だんだんお腹が空いてきましたね",
      "startTime": 236.7333218892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "食事を忘れるのは、俺も人のことは言えないけどな……\n事務所も閉めるから、今日は切り上げよう",
      "startTime": 246.299992625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-ktn020.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、もう少しだけやらせて下さい\nあと何回かやれば、出来るようになると思うんです",
      "startTime": 253.3333218892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃の意気込みは分かるが\nオーバーワークで当日倒れたら、元も子もないだろ",
      "startTime": 259.5666552226,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "（麻奈もそれで入院したことがあったし）\n（琴乃も……思い詰めると、一人で無茶しがちだからな）",
      "startTime": 266.4333218892,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8766.666666700019,
          "startTime": 275.1999885559
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 12633.333333400004,
          "startTime": 279.0666552226
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-ktn021.m4a",
      "text": "ですが、もうライブまで時間もありませんし……\n……あれ？　みんなからメッセが……",
      "startTime": 276.8999885559,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-ktn022.m4a",
      "text": "「琴乃ちゃん、まだスタジオで練習してるの？」\n「今日の自主練は一時間までという約束です」",
      "startTime": 286.1000007629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
